<html>
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<title>Password reset instructions for morethingsneed.to</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>Password reset instructions for morethingsneed.to</h1>
		
		<p>Greetings <%= @user.username %>,</p>
		
		<p>A request to reset your password has been made on <a href="http://morethingsneed.to/">morethingsneed.to</a>. In order to reset your current password and change it to a new one, please visit the following link:</p>
		
		<p><a href="<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.perishable_token) %>"><%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.perishable_token) %></a></p>

		<p>
			Try not to be so forgetful next time!<br>
			The morethingsneed.to team
		</p>
	</body>
</html>